1
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:47,440
Your Majesty.

2
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,360
Greetings, Sister.

3
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:51,600
Hmph.

4
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,760
Hmph. Your Majesty.

5
00:00:57,760 --> 00:00:58,440
Hmph.

6
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,000
Didn't you say yesterday

7
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:05,530
that you wanted to try some new tricks with me?

8
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,640
Why are you staring blankly today?

9
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:11,000
Why are you with another sister today?

10
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,840
I guess I came

11
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,039
at a bad time.

12
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:15,560
Hmph.

13
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:17,680
Your Majesty,

14
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:20,530
where are the rest of the name tags?

15
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,860
What name tags? You are not allowed to flip them.

16
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,680
How dare she knock over the green-headed tags

17
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,160
to monopolize His Majesty.

18
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,160
This Cangyue's

19
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,960
good days are over.

20
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:31,680
Lady Cang,

21
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,640
the Emperor cannot favor you alone.

22
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:37,220
You should show equal favor to everyone.

23
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,360
Humph.

24
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,200
If I knew other sisters were coming,

25
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:43,560
I wouldn't have come today.

26
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,600
Your Majesty.

27
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,640
Haven't I already flipped the tags?

28
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,039
Why aren't you announcing the names?

29
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:51,479
Your Majesty, this...

30
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,080
Eunuch Sun,

31
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,410
do you want to watch too?

32
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,400
Oh dear,

33
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,400
I wouldn't dare.

34
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,960
Your Majesty, please enjoy yourself.

35
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,360
Go.

36
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:06,840
I will take my leave.

37
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,620
These concubines,

38
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,740
do you really not like any of them?

39
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,440
They are just a bunch of women

40
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,400
sent by my aunt.

41
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,079
Women sent by your aunt are still women.

42
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:28,240
Besides, they are so pretty.

43
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,720
If you win them over,

44
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:32,380
they could even help you instigate a rebellion.

45
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,960
Acting is acting.

46
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:42,020
What are you doing with your hands? Where are you putting them?

47
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,240
You don't look the part.

48
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,640
If I don't help you,

49
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:50,640
you'll blow your cover.

50
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:59,440
You play the role of a tyrant quite well.

51
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,280
However,

52
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:04,370
if you want to find an actor like yourself,

53
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:06,680
who is equally matched,

54
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:10,760
those concubines act much better than I do.

55
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,760
After all, I still have to rely on him to deal with the Grand Princess.

56
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:20,960
I can't piss him off.

57
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,360
Alright, I know.

58
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:31,140
They were all sent by the Grand Princess.

59
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,480
I won't taint you.

60
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:34,960
You know...

61
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,970
Walls have ears.

62
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:54,360
Who says my acting is bad?

63
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:57,000
Look. The fish

64
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,880
took the bait, didn't it?

65
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:36,080
Oh, stop looking.

66
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,920
These paintings are shoddy.

67
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,360
What's so good about them?

68
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,640
Come, sit down first.

69
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,040
Come on.

70
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:52,020
Your Majesty, they have arrived.

71
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,400
Cang Yue

72
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,260
greets Your Highness.

73
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,080
I will soon

74
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:06,440
select three new male concubines.

75
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,360
You are just in time.

76
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:12,960
Help me see which one is suitable.

77
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,360
Your Highness,

78
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,600
a constant companion

79
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:32,320
cannot be chosen from portraits.

80
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,720
Very well.

81
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:51,159
Ah, I am thirsty.

82
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:30,480
Your Highness, please have some tea.

83
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,920
You are quite tolerant.

84
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:39,080
No wonder His Majesty favors only you.

85
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,640
It seems that in the future,

86
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:45,960
His Majesty will have another sweet companion by his side.

87
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:51,680
I have prepared a cup of poisoned wine

88
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,800
and a lifetime of wealth.

89
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,960
Make your choice.

90
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,400
If you are smart,

91
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:04,130
you should know what to choose.

92
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:09,880
Cangyue thanks Your Highness for your appreciation.

93
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,320
I will do my utmost

94
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:14,720
and will not hesitate even if I have to die ten thousand times.

95
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:45,440
To have a new partner poison the Emperor.

96
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:49,480
Si Xinglan couldn't be that stupid.

97
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:28,160
Your Highness, as you instructed,

98
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,120
I watched Cangyue

99
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,850
put the poison into the porridge with my own eyes.

100
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,720
However,

101
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:38,559
I didn't see anything unusual with His Majesty.

102
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,799
Could it be some new trick?
